{"type": "article", "id": 27846, "title": "一体化写字桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-07T06:51:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703120018fd46B2nPhR5puwyT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>来自荷兰的 Frans Willigers 最近设计了一款混合型的桌椅 <a href=\"http://willigers.com/?portfolio=last-writing-desk\">Last Writing Desk</a>，在他眼中这种一体化的写字桌将会取代传统的办公家具。桌子和椅子通过斜坡连为一体，营造出一种特别的层次感，下方则使用四根不锈钢腿支撑。Willigers 采用简洁的设计使它便于搬运，适用于图书馆、机场这样的公共场所。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120016am95uvBToPys6X3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6965812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120016aCJcriN6B4h7yYVL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6517094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120016klNjGQmKLxhz1woH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72115385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120017qsi65pz40nTEZNCQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}